headline: Phillips 66 raises quarterly dividend to $1.27 per share
summary: The board of directors of Phillips 66 (PSX) has declared a quarterly dividend of $1.27 per share on Phillips 66 common stock, representing a $0.07 increase. headline: Murphy USA Q4 Earnings Beat Estimates as Fuel Margins Rise
summary: MUSA tops Q4 earnings estimates as fuel margins expand and merchandise sales rise, lifting total fuel contribution despite softer petroleum revenues.

headline: Phillips 66 (PSX) Shows Earnings Momentum Amid Strategic Portfolio Transformation
summary: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) is one of the best long-term retirement stocks.
